		<title>貧者の兵器</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://text.baldanders.info/remark/2019/09/poor-mans-weapons/" />
		<id>tag:text.Baldanders.info,2019-09-23:/remark/2019/09/poor-mans-weapons/</id>
